1
00:00:13,059 --> 00:00:14,820
Actually, you and Ji Xiaoxue

2
00:00:15,180 --> 00:00:16,140
are siblings.

3
00:00:16,860 --> 00:00:17,939
What nonsense are you talking about?

4
00:00:18,140 --> 00:00:19,739
My parents died long ago.

5
00:00:19,739 --> 00:00:21,379
I grew up in an orphanage.

6
00:00:21,379 --> 00:00:22,860
How could I possibly be his sister?

7
00:00:23,099 --> 00:00:24,379
If you keep talking nonsense

8
00:00:24,660 --> 00:00:26,539
and tarnishing Xiaoxue and the Gu family's reputation,

9
00:00:27,099 --> 00:00:28,300
I won't be so nice.

10
00:00:29,340 --> 00:00:30,379
She's not talking nonsense.

11
00:00:35,220 --> 00:00:36,099
Xiaoxue,

12
00:00:36,739 --> 00:00:38,020
you are my daughter.

13
00:00:39,859 --> 00:00:41,300
Your last name is not Ji.

14
00:00:41,779 --> 00:00:42,580
Your last name is Liu.

15
00:00:43,300 --> 00:00:44,379
You take your mother's last name.

16
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:46,540
After your mother died,

17
00:00:47,139 --> 00:00:48,260
you went to the orphanage

18
00:00:49,020 --> 00:00:50,139
and then changed your last name to Ji.

19
00:00:51,620 --> 00:00:52,459
Am I right?

20
00:00:54,300 --> 00:00:56,739
Yes, my last name is Liu.

21
00:00:57,139 --> 00:00:59,179
But how does that prove I'm your daughter?

22
00:00:59,580 --> 00:01:00,859
You've asked me many times

23
00:01:01,459 --> 00:01:02,900
why I'm so good to you.

24
00:01:04,620 --> 00:01:06,059
The first time I saw you,

25
00:01:06,540 --> 00:01:07,380
I felt

26
00:01:07,779 --> 00:01:09,659
you looked a lot like your mother.

27
00:01:15,180 --> 00:01:16,380
Your mother was also

28
00:01:16,700 --> 00:01:18,219
a servant in the Gu family.

29
00:01:19,859 --> 00:01:21,340
We fell in love secretly.

30
00:01:31,260 --> 00:01:32,820
But due to family pressure,

31
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:35,019
I couldn't marry your mother.

32
00:01:36,219 --> 00:01:38,100
When your mother was four months pregnant,

33
00:01:38,779 --> 00:01:39,859
she left without a word.

34
00:01:41,380 --> 00:01:43,779
Later, she sent me a letter

35
00:01:44,180 --> 00:01:45,499
and a photo of you,

36
00:01:46,779 --> 00:01:47,980
saying you were born

37
00:01:48,460 --> 00:01:50,419
with a snowflake birthmark on your chest,

38
00:01:51,740 --> 00:01:53,579
so she named you Xiaoxue.

39
00:02:28,060 --> 00:02:28,859
From now on,

40
00:02:29,940 --> 00:02:32,299
if anyone dares to bother Xiaoxue,

41
00:02:34,139 --> 00:02:35,299
I won't let them off the hook.

42
00:02:40,579 --> 00:02:41,459
It's not true.

43
00:02:43,380 --> 00:02:44,339
You all lied to me.

44
00:02:48,419 --> 00:02:49,500
You all lied to me!

45
00:02:52,339 --> 00:02:53,179
It's not true!

46
00:03:05,899 --> 00:03:06,780
You know,

47
00:03:07,700 --> 00:03:09,380
I don't want to marry Xia Wanqing.

48
00:03:10,419 --> 00:03:11,579
I want to be with you.

49
00:03:13,220 --> 00:03:14,540
If I don't marry her,

50
00:03:15,380 --> 00:03:16,619
will you be with me?

51
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:24,859
No matter what happens in the future,

52
00:03:25,739 --> 00:03:27,500
don't ever kick me out, okay?

53
00:03:39,780 --> 00:03:40,739
So,

54
00:03:41,299 --> 00:03:43,179
you knew they were siblings all along?

55
00:03:45,299 --> 00:03:47,739
Then why did you make me drive Ji Xiaoxue away?

56
00:03:49,579 --> 00:03:50,940
Because separation breeds longing.

57
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:52,419
Longing

58
00:03:53,260 --> 00:03:54,299
leads to appreciation.

59
00:04:03,859 --> 00:04:05,139
You're quite the strategist.

60
00:04:07,339 --> 00:04:08,339
Because only this way

61
00:04:09,380 --> 00:04:10,380
can I marry you.

62
00:04:16,380 --> 00:04:17,500
I didn't say

63
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:19,380
I would marry you.

64
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:24,620
As long as you're willing to marry me,

65
00:04:25,539 --> 00:04:26,620
I can give you anything.

66
00:05:10,659 --> 00:05:12,139
This was quite sudden.

67
00:05:13,099 --> 00:05:13,979
I thought

68
00:05:14,979 --> 00:05:16,779
I'd never see you or your mom again.

69
00:05:17,180 --> 00:05:19,500
Didn't you ever think about looking for us?

70
00:05:19,779 --> 00:05:20,620
I did.

71
00:05:21,579 --> 00:05:22,820
Your mom didn't want to see me.

72
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:24,180
That's an excuse.

73
00:05:24,940 --> 00:05:26,019
You could have not found us,

74
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:28,420
but you shouldn't have stopped looking.

75
00:05:29,500 --> 00:05:31,180
You never truly considered

76
00:05:31,180 --> 00:05:32,060
looking for us.

77
00:05:32,940 --> 00:05:34,779
I was under a lot of pressure back then.

78
00:05:35,620 --> 00:05:36,339
I'm sorry.

79
00:05:37,539 --> 00:05:38,700
You don't need to apologize to me.

80
00:05:39,060 --> 00:05:40,019
In my world,

81
00:05:40,019 --> 00:05:41,420
I don't have this relationship,

82
00:05:42,860 --> 00:05:44,139
nor do I have a father.

83
00:05:45,260 --> 00:05:45,940
Xiaoxue,

84
00:05:46,940 --> 00:05:49,019
I don't want to force you to accept me as your father.

85
00:05:49,659 --> 00:05:51,420
I just want to make up for what I owe

86
00:05:52,139 --> 00:05:53,539
to you and your mother.

87
00:05:57,740 --> 00:05:58,459
This time,

88
00:05:59,339 --> 00:06:00,820
you can come to our Gu family again.

89
00:06:02,019 --> 00:06:03,899
It means that God wants to give me a chance.

90
00:06:05,979 --> 00:06:08,139
Can you give me a chance to make up for you?

91
00:06:13,300 --> 00:06:13,940
Xiaoxue,

92
00:06:15,180 --> 00:06:16,700
I know you hate me.

93
00:06:17,539 --> 00:06:19,300
I really love your mother very much.

94
00:06:19,779 --> 00:06:21,459
I'm still single now.

95
00:06:21,899 --> 00:06:23,820
This time, I went abroad

96
00:06:24,019 --> 00:06:25,539
and checked my body again.

97
00:06:25,740 --> 00:06:27,099
The situation is not very good.

98
00:06:28,180 --> 00:06:29,860
I don't have much time left.

99
00:06:30,899 --> 00:06:32,979
But fortunately,

100
00:06:33,139 --> 00:06:34,219
I met you.

101
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:36,979
I sincerely hope

102
00:06:37,740 --> 00:06:38,979
I can do something for you.

103
00:06:42,099 --> 00:06:44,300
If you want to do something for me, that's fine.

104
00:06:45,899 --> 00:06:46,539
Then...

105
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:48,219
What?

106
00:06:49,260 --> 00:06:50,820
You give your shares to her?

107
00:06:51,219 --> 00:06:51,899
Right.

108
00:06:52,539 --> 00:06:53,659
I have already decided

109
00:06:53,659 --> 00:06:56,459
to give all my shares to Ji Xiaoxue.

110
00:06:57,620 --> 00:06:58,779
From today on,

111
00:06:59,459 --> 00:07:01,700
Xiaoxue will be a shareholder of the Gu Group.

112
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:37,899
Xiaoxue, pass me the candy.

113
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:42,300
Are you deaf?

114
00:07:43,139 --> 00:07:44,700
Didn't you hear her asking for candy?

115
00:07:45,019 --> 00:07:47,740
How can you let the Third Miss Gu do this?

116
00:08:12,779 --> 00:08:13,779
Have you heard?

117
00:08:14,180 --> 00:08:17,620
Ji Xiaoxue is the Old Master Gu's biological daughter.

118
00:08:17,979 --> 00:08:19,420
I've heard it for a long time.

119
00:08:19,539 --> 00:08:21,899
It's said she was born to a maid years ago.

120
00:08:22,779 --> 00:08:24,260
And I heard

121
00:08:24,459 --> 00:08:25,700
she almost

122
00:08:25,779 --> 00:08:28,260
got together with Mr. Gu.

123
00:08:28,899 --> 00:08:30,780
Really? That's so dramatic.

124
00:08:38,499 --> 00:08:40,739
What does that slut have?

125
00:08:42,099 --> 00:08:44,259
Gu Qisen and Gu Chengyan are both around her.

126
00:08:44,259 --> 00:08:46,420
If Ji Xiaoxue and Gu Chengyan join forces,

127
00:08:46,979 --> 00:08:48,499
I'm afraid my chances of winning are slim.

128
00:08:50,219 --> 00:08:52,900
You must hold on to Xia Wanqing now.

129
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:54,780
The Xia family behind her

130
00:08:54,780 --> 00:08:56,140
is our only support.

131
00:08:57,660 --> 00:08:58,619
I see, Mom.
